<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/peter-kyle> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Peter Kyle was appointed Secretary of State for Business and Trade and President of the Board of Trade on 5 September 2025. He was previously Secretary of State for Science, Innovation and Technology from 5 July 2024 to 5 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Hove and Portslade in July 2024."@en .
